## Assertions

### Selector Assertions

```ruby
# Element exists
assert_selector "h1", text: "Title"
assert_selector ".article", count: 3
assert_selector "form#new_article"

# Element doesn't exist
assert_no_selector ".error-message"
assert_no_selector "button", text: "Delete"

# CSS selector
assert_selector "div.card > h2.title"

# XPath selector
assert_selector :xpath, "//div[@id='content']"
```

### Text Assertions

```ruby
# Text present on page
assert_text "Article created successfully"
assert_text /Published \d+ minutes ago/

# Text not present
assert_no_text "Error"
assert_no_text "Failed"
```

### Link Assertions

```ruby
# Link exists
assert_link "Edit"
assert_link "Delete", href: article_path(@article)

# Link doesn't exist
assert_no_link "Admin Panel"
```

### Button Assertions

```ruby
# Button exists
assert_button "Submit"
assert_button "Save", disabled: false

# Button doesn't exist
assert_no_button "Delete"
```

### Field Assertions

```ruby
# Field exists
assert_field "Email"
assert_field "Email", with: "user@example.com"

# Checked checkbox
assert_checked_field "Published"
assert_unchecked_field "Featured"

# Selected option
assert_select "Category", selected: "Technology"
```

